1. Upoznao sam *Londonu* prošlog ljeta. (I met London last summer.)
2. Ona je iz *Londona*. (She is from London.)
3. *Londonom* se prošetao u sred noći. (He took a walk through London in the middle of the night.)
4. Da li si posjetio *Londonu*? (Have you visited London?)
5. Oni su se uputili prema *Londonu*. (They headed towards London.)
6. *London* je poznat po svojim muzejima. (London is known for its museums.)
7. Njihova putovanja obično počinju iz *Londona*. (Their travels usually start from London.)
8. *Londonu* se divim zbog njegove arhitekture. (I admire London for its architecture.)
9. U *Londonu* sam bio tri dana. (I was in London for three days.)
10. Njihov cilj je da posjete sve znamenitosti *Londona*. (Their goal is to visit all the landmarks of London.)

(Note: In Serbian, "Londona" is the genitive case of "London".)